    "nabardSupport": "NABARD has significantly contributed to the preservation and promotion of Sambhal Bone Craft: GI Registration Support: Assistance with documentation, awareness campaigns, and ensuring proper legal protection of the craft. Skill Development Programs: Conducted training workshops to improve artisans' techniques and encourage innovative product designs. Market Linkages: Supported artisans by facilitating participation in national and international exhibitions and fairs.",
